data.description: Owner Finance! Dueno a dueno! No Banks, no hassle! Honey stop the car, this is our chance to stop renting and become homeowners! The location here is PRIME,3 Min from The Forum, 20 Min from New Braunfels, 20 Min from Downtown San Antonio. As you drive into the neighborhood you will quickly feel less and less in the city. This stunning home boasts two stories, 4 bedrooms, and 2.5 baths. The main floor features a remarkable open-concept layout, and the master bedroom! The kitchen, perfect for any aspiring chef, is equipped with energy-efficient appliances, and granite countertops. Upstairs, walk directly into a large game area along with 3 bedrooms, and 1 Bath.
